籤詩版本二:
Puhi mai ka mahina i ka lani a mālie ka hale, ʻaʻole i paʻa au i nā ao a me ka noe a hāʻule i loko o ke koma.
E pule ʻoe no ka maluhia o ka noʻonoʻo, Yunxia Powder, hoʻololi i ke aloha i kēia manawa, a kākau i puke ma ka hale.
詩意:
Ma kēia hexagram, uhi ʻia nā ao a me ka noe i ka mahina.
E hoʻomau i nā ala kahiko inā ʻaʻole pono nā mea.
籤詩故事一:
◇ Ua pepehi ʻia ʻo He Wenxiu
I ka manawa o Jiajing o ka Ming, ua hoʻokumu ʻia ʻo He Wenxiu e nā kuhina hoʻopunipuni a ua pilikia kona ʻohana. Ua hoʻopiʻi wahaheʻe ʻia ʻo He Wenxiu e ka mea hoʻoweliweli ʻo Zhang Tang a ua hoʻopaʻahao ʻia ʻo ia ma hope mai ua hoʻopakele ʻia ʻo ia a lilo i kiaʻāina ma hope o ka hala ʻana i ka hoʻokolokolo. Ua ʻike ʻo Wenxiu i kahi o Wang Lanying a ua ʻaʻahu ʻo ia e like me ke kilokilo e ʻike ai. Ua hui hou ʻia lāua ʻelua, a ua pepehi ʻia ʻo Zhang Tang.
聖意: ʻAʻole ʻoluʻolu ma ka home, pule au no ka palekana, pilikia kālā, pilikia ʻoihana, pilikia male, nele ʻo Liujia, pedestrians blocking fields, silkworm pōʻino, hōʻino holoholona, ​​nalo nā kānaka, nā hoʻopiʻi lehulehu, migration, nalowale waiwai, maʻi, Yan'an mauna ilina pono. e hooponopono
古人: Ua pepehi ʻia ʻo He Wenxiu
